Date: Sun, 29 Mar 2026 11:50:19 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] fix: dynamic mcp list + /usr/bin/curl path + dns via
 Command
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- mcp list: fully dynamic, queries mcpd services/list, probes each service [live/down]
- Removed KNOWN_SERVICES hardcoded constant — zero static service list
- curl: /usr/bin/curl instead of bare curl (fixes "not found" on ACOS)
- dns: Command::new("dns") instead of dns: scheme (scheme doesn't exist)
- Verified in QEMU: 19 services [live], dns resolves 104.18.26.120, ping 0% loss
